{
  "name": "小红书创作者分析工作流",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "xiaohongshu-analysis",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "responseData": "firstEntryJson"
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "接收小红书数据",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        280,
        300
      ],
      "webhookId": "xhs-creator-analysis"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "你是一个专业的社交媒体数据分析师，专门分析小红书创作者的内容和表现。请根据以下创作者数据进行深度分析，生成一份专业的分析报告。\n\n# 创作者数据\n用户名：{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.userName }}\n小红书号：{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.userId }}\n订阅数：{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.subscribers }}\n粉丝数：{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.followers }}\n获赞数：{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.likes }}\n档案地址：{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.profileUrl }}\n\n# 所有标题列表\n{{ $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.allTitles.join('\\n') }}\n\n# 前10篇热门笔记详情\n{% for note in $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body.top10Notes %}\n标题：{{ note.title }}\n描述：{{ note.desc }}\n点赞：{{ note.like }}\n收藏：{{ note.collect }}\n---\n{% endfor %}\n\n# 分析要求\n请从以下5个维度进行专业分析，生成一份完整的创作者分析报告：\n\n## 1. 数据概览\n- 分析创作者的基础数据表现（粉丝数、获赞数、互动率等）\n- 评估账号的影响力水平\n- 对比行业平均水平（如果可以推断的话）\n\n## 2. 赛道分析\n- 根据笔记内容识别创作者的主要内容赛道\n- 分析内容分布和专业领域\n- 评估赛道选择的合理性和发展潜力\n\n## 3. 标题风格分析\n- 分析标题的语言风格和表达方式\n- 识别常用的标题模板和套路\n- 评估标题的吸引力和SEO友好度\n\n## 4. 笔记风格分析\n- 分析笔记描述的写作风格\n- 识别常用话题标签和关键词\n- 评估内容的专业度和可读性\n\n## 5. 热门笔记分析\n- 分析前10篇笔记的表现数据\n- 识别爆款内容的共同特征\n- 提供内容优化建议\n\n# 输出格式要求\n请以专业的分析报告格式输出，使用markdown语法，包含清晰的章节结构和数据支撑。报告应该客观、专业、有深度，能够为创作者提供有价值的洞察和建议。\n\n现在请开始分析并生成报告。",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "你是一个专业的小红书数据分析师，擅长分析创作者的内容策略、受众特征和商业价值。请确保分析结果专业、客观、有深度。"
        }
      },
      "id": "ai-agent-analysis",
      "name": "AI创作者分析",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        500,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "deepseek/deepseek-v3.2"
      },
      "id": "openrouter-chat-model",
      "name": "OpenRouter DeepSeek模型",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenRouter",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        500,
        160
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const webhookData = $('接收小红书数据').first().json.body;\nconst aiAnalysisResult = $('AI创作者分析').first().json;\n\nconst bodyData = webhookData.body || webhookData;\n\nconst authorData = {\n  user_name: bodyData.userName || '',\n  user_xhs_id: bodyData.userId || '',\n  subscribers: parseInt(bodyData.subscribers) || 0,\n  followers: parseInt(bodyData.followers) || 0,\n  likes: parseInt(bodyData.likes) || 0,\n  profile_url: bodyData.profileUrl || '',\n  report: aiAnalysisResult.output || aiAnalysisResult.text || JSON.stringify(aiAnalysisResult)\n};\n\nconst top10Titles = bodyData.top10Notes ? bodyData.top10Notes.map(note => note.title) : [];\nconst otherTitles = bodyData.allTitles ? bodyData.allTitles.filter(title => !top10Titles.includes(title)) : [];\nauthorData.other_notes = otherTitles;\n\nconst notesData = [];\nif (bodyData.top10Notes && Array.isArray(bodyData.top10Notes)) {\n  bodyData.top10Notes.forEach(note => {\n    const noteData = {\n      title: note.title,\n      description: note.desc || '',\n      likes: parseInt(note.like) || 0,\n      collects: parseInt(note.collect) || 0,\n      is_top10: true,\n      raw_json: note\n    };\n    notesData.push(noteData);\n  });\n}\n\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      authorData: authorData,\n      notesData: notesData,\n      originalData: bodyData,\n      analysisResult: aiAnalysisResult\n    }\n  }\n];"
      },
      "id": "data-processor",
      "name": "数据处理器",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        720,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $credentials.supabaseApi.host }}/rest/v1/authors?user_xhs_id=eq.{{ $json.authorData.user_xhs_id }}&select=id",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "supabaseApi",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "apikey",
              "value": "={{ $credentials.supabaseApi.serviceRole }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ $credentials.supabaseApi.serviceRole }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "check-author-exists",
      "name": "查询作者是否存在",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        940,
        300
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "supabaseApi": {
          "id": "CE5OpE28TxbcI9h2",
          "name": "Supabase account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const authorData = $('数据处理器').first().json.authorData;\nconst notesData = $('数据处理器').first().json.notesData;\nconst originalData = $('数据处理器').first().json.originalData;\nconst analysisResult = $('数据处理器').first().json.analysisResult;\n\nconst queryResult = $input.first().json;\nconst authorExists = Array.isArray(queryResult) && queryResult.length > 0;\nconst existingAuthorId = authorExists ? queryResult[0].id : null;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    authorExists,\n    existingAuthorId,\n    authorData,\n    notesData,\n    originalData,\n    analysisResult\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "process-query-result",
      "name": "处理查询结果",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1050,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "version": 2,
            "leftValue": "",
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "author-exists-condition",
              "operator": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "operation": "true",
                "singleValue": true
              },
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.authorExists }}",
              "rightValue": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      },
